<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Tickets To Mars</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}


html{
scroll-behavior:smooth;
}


body{

background:#050505;
color:white;

}


/* SPACE STARS */

body::before{

content:"";

position:fixed;

width:100%;
height:100%;

background:
radial-gradient(circle,white 1px,transparent 1px);

background-size:50px 50px;

opacity:.2;

z-index:-1;

}



/* NAV */

nav{

position:fixed;

top:0;

width:100%;

padding:20px;

display:flex;

justify-content:space-between;

background:
rgba(0,0,0,.7);

backdrop-filter:blur(10px);

z-index:10;

}


nav h2{

color:#ff6033;

}


nav a{

color:white;

text-decoration:none;

margin:15px;

}



/* SECTIONS */

section{

min-height:100vh;

padding:100px 8%;

display:flex;

align-items:center;

justify-content:center;

flex-direction:column;

}



/* HERO */

.hero{

text-align:center;

}


.hero h1{

font-size:80px;

color:#ff6033;

text-shadow:
0 0 30px red;

}


.hero p{

font-size:25px;

max-width:700px;

margin:30px;

}


.button{

background:#ff6033;

padding:15px 40px;

border-radius:40px;

color:white;

text-decoration:none;

font-weight:bold;

}



/* TICKETS */


.ticket-container{

display:grid;

grid-template-columns:
repeat(3,1fr);

gap:30px;

width:100%;

}


.card{

background:
rgba(255,255,255,.08);

padding:30px;

border-radius:25px;

border:
1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);

transition:.4s;

}


.card:hover{

transform:
translateY(-15px);

}


.card h2{

color:#ff7040;

}



.price{

font-size:40px;

margin:20px 0;

}



/* TIMELINE */

.timeline{

max-width:900px;

}


.step{

margin:30px;

padding:25px;

border-left:
4px solid #ff6033;

background:
rgba(255,255,255,.05);

}



/* COLONY */


.colony{

display:grid;

grid-template-columns:
repeat(2,1fr);

gap:30px;

}


.city{

padding:30px;

background:#151515;

border-radius:20px;

}


.city span{

color:#ff6033;

}



/* FOOTER */

footer{

padding:40px;

text-align:center;

background:#000;

}



/* MOBILE */

@media(max-width:800px){


.hero h1{

font-size:45px;

}


.ticket-container,
.colony{

grid-template-columns:1fr;

}


nav{

flex-direction:column;

}


}

</style>

</head>



<body>


<nav>

<h2>MARS PASS</h2>

<div>

<a href="#tickets">Tickets</a>
<a href="#mission">Mission</a>
<a href="#colony">Colony</a>

</div>

</nav>



<!-- SECTION 1 -->

<section class="hero">


<h1>YOUR TICKET TO MARS</h1>


<p>

Become one of the first humans to travel beyond Earth.
Reserve your seat aboard the next generation Starship.

</p>


<a class="button" href="#tickets">
Reserve Seat
</a>


</section>




<!-- SECTION 2 -->

<section id="tickets">


<h1>Choose Your Mission</h1>


<div class="ticket-container">


<div class="card">

<h2>Explorer</h2>

<p>
Basic Mars transportation package.
</p>

<div class="price">
$250K
</div>

<p>
✓ Starship Flight<br>
✓ Mars Landing<br>
✓ Habitat Access
</p>

</div>




<div class="card">

<h2>Pioneer</h2>

<p>
Build the first Mars civilization.
</p>

<div class="price">
$500K
</div>

<p>
✓ Private Cabin<br>
✓ Science Missions<br>
✓ Colony Training
</p>

</div>




<div class="card">

<h2>Founder</h2>

<p>
Create the future Mars city.
</p>

<div class="price">
$1M
</div>

<p>
✓ Large Habitat<br>
✓ Research Labs<br>
✓ Leadership Role
</p>

</div>


</div>


</section>





<!-- SECTION 3 -->


<section id="mission">


<h1>Mars Mission Timeline</h1>


<div class="timeline">


<div class="step">

<h2>2026</h2>

<p>
Starship technology development and testing.
</p>

</div>


<div class="step">

<h2>2030</h2>

<p>
First cargo missions establish Mars infrastructure.
</p>

</div>



<div class="step">

<h2>2035</h2>

<p>
First human settlements begin.
</p>

</div>



<div class="step">

<h2>2050</h2>

<p>
A permanent Mars civilization grows.
</p>

</div>


</div>


</section>






<!-- SECTION 4 -->

<section id="colony">


<h1>Future Mars Cities</h1>


<div class="colony">


<div class="city">

<h2>Olympus City</h2>

<span>500,000 Residents</span>

<p>
Located near Olympus Mons.
</p>

</div>


<div class="city">

<h2>Ares Capital</h2>

<span>Mars Headquarters</span>

<p>
Government and research center.
</p>

</div>


<div class="city">

<h2>Valles Prime</h2>

<span>Scientific Colony</span>

<p>
Built inside Valles Marineris.
</p>

</div>


<div class="city">

<h2>Elysium Hub</h2>

<span>Industrial Zone</span>

<p>
Robotics and manufacturing.
</p>

</div>


</div>


</section>






<!-- SECTION 5 -->

<section>


<h1>The Next Human Adventure</h1>


<p style="max-width:700px;text-align:center;font-size:22px">

Earth was our beginning.
Mars will be our next chapter.
The first explorers will not just visit Mars —
they will build a new world.

</p>


<a class="button">
Join Mars Mission
</a>


</section>



<footer>

© 2050 Mars Pass | Humanity Beyond Earth

</footer>



</body>

</html>
